        <h4 align = "center"> <text class = "text-nidheim"> Nidheim </text> </h4>
        <p align = "justify"> In the midst of the icy plains and tundras, there is a civilization that, following the pure meaning of strength and survival, is able to sustain itself. The Nidheim tribe is characterized by the value of power and, by many, its members are seen as barbarians who care nothing about conflict and conquest. </p>
        <p align = "justify"> In front of the dragon, not even the ice will be an obstacle. The flame burning in your heart is able to overcome all obstacles and melt everything that seeks to oppose. A member of Nidheim never allows himself to be overcome and sees strength as the determining factor in all cases. If not for absolute defeat, he will never be able to prostrate himself in front of others, since violence is his dialogue. </p>

