        <h4 align = "center"> <text class = "text-nidheim">Nidheim:</text> Nidlebens beliefs </h4>
        <p align = "justify"> The nidlebens come from a cold and hostile region; and so are his people and religion. Unlike Kaus or Uria, which have well-established religious systems, formulated rules of coexistence and even names for their religions, there is almost no writing on the beliefs of the inhabitants of Nidheim. Everything we know is passed on through songs and stories. </p>
        <p align = "justify"> They are known to believe that there are two divine dragons competing. The lord of cold and the lady of heat; The lord of cold is a terrible silver dragon that is apparently getting the better of it; while the lady of heat is a golden dragon and favorable to humans. In addition to the dragon gods, there are a lot of magical creatures in their folklore, some of which are responsible for creating and maintaining life and death. </p>
