        <h4 align = "center"> <text class = "text-nidheim">Nidheim:</text> Political System </h4>
        <p align = "justify"> In Nidheim, there are no governors. There are only 3 positions you can be in: civilian, slave and priest. Note that the civilian is not the opposite of the military, but of the slave. The priest lives on donations from the people himself - even receiving slaves -, and intermediates contact with Lady of Heat, holds festivals on commemorative days, funerals for those who die outside the battlefield, and so on. </p>
